social_posts.post_text: I hate it when I’m making milkshakes and the boys show up to the yard
not wearing green but still your lucky charm 🌈 🍀 🎈

Top 10 in my first hooters pageant of many to come! Thank you to everyone who came to support me and for everyone who donated to give a hoot! I’m so glad I am part of a company who gives back to the community and raises money in such a fun way! @hooterscasting
have a holly jolly Christmas, xoxo 💋
